<i>verb</i>: 비하하다 [비ː하하다] <br>
<ul><li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비하하다 [비ː하하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. self-deprecate</dd><br>
<dd>자기 자신을 낮추다.</dd><br>
<dd>To belittle oneself.</dd><br>
<dd>2. abase; belittle</dd><br>
<dd>하찮게 여겨 낮추다.</dd><br>
<dd>To belittle someone and consider him/her as trivial.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>